<del rend="strikethrough"> etl </del> ye mandat ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_185_r1l19">vns <expan>kom<ex>m</ex>en</expan> vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>pfarr<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> . dıe vns dıe denn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_185_r1l20">fürbas fürbracht haben / <expan>Dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mandat / in <expan>eıne<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> form </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_185_r1l21">lawten / vnd als vns dunkt <expan>fremdıklıch<ex>er</ex></expan> denn wır vor <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_185_r1l22">als ır an der 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>eıngeſloſſ<ex>en</ex></expan></del> <expan>abſchr<ex>ift</ex></expan> / <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mandat eıns . Hıerynnen </ab>
