</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Ersamer und <expan>l<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>ne</expan> doctor, es sind
                            <expan>newlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ye mandat zu uns
                            <expan>kom<ex>m</ex>en</expan> und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>pfarr<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>
<expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan>, die uns die denn fürbas fürbracht haben.
                                <expan>Dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mandat in
                            <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> form lawten und als uns dunkt
                                <expan>fremdiklich<ex>er</ex></expan>, denn wir vor
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, als ir an der
                            <expan>abschr<ex>ift</ex></expan>
<expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mandat eins hierynnen
                                <expan>versloss<ex>en</ex></expan> wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan> mugt. Das tun wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>zu wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz ir darauff bedacht sein und uns
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> rat und <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
                        darinn <expan>verschr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wellet, als wir ewch
                                <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan>, daran beweiset ir uns
                                <expan>sund<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> und
                        <expan>wolgefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Galli.</ab>
</div>
